#G20India has left behind a historic legacy of hope, harmony and inclusivity for humanity. 

The roaring success of India’s Presidency led by PM @narendramodi ji is a matter of pride for all Indians. Unanimity for ‘Planet, People, Peace & Prosperity’ is a bold reflection of PM Modi’s statesmanship and India as a lighthouse of global peace and well-being. From the ‘Konark Sun Wheel’ of Odisha to the ancient ‘Nalanda University’ in Bihar, PM Modi has put the spotlight back on India’s democratic and knowledge traditions as well as civilisational ethos to harmonise the world as #OneFamily having #OneFuture.

Hon. PM @narendramodi ji and global leaders pay solemn tributes to Mahatma Gandhi ji at #Rajghat.

PM Modi’s call of human-centric globalisation leaving none behind and moving ahead with the spirit of #SabkaSaath has resonated with the world. India’s Presidency under the leadership of PM Modi has made the #G20 family more inclusive and strengthened India’s stature as a credible voice of the Global South.

Odisha’s magnificent culture and heritage finds a place of pride at #G20India.
